{"tid":1566844,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"見到3個傻仔拎住英國旗行龍翔道上畢架山","createTime":"2019-09-13T18:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T05:23:55.000Z","uid":254330,"like":359,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"641f382f8a7fdef632da5f24ac7669a67e62c10c","tid":1566844,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:49:27.000Z","msg":"個傻仔就係樓豬同佢班friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班傻仔拎住2支英國旗,1支港英旗周圍走<br />\n<br />\n本身去獅子山,因為山腳已經full人行唔到,所以轉場,經龍翔道行去上畢架山<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,好撚遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QqTvo1U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQqTvo1U.png&h=d8cfbc21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwxoJ16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwxoJ16.png&h=6e306786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後行上畢架山<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U6euEBH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU6euEBH.png&h=611cf050&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GoX4tu5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGoX4tu5.jpg&h=72360c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個月亮好圓呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HUCTmQL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHUCTmQL.png&h=fefe1792&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDqYxXu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDqYxXu.jpg&h=180b942c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O902faR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO902faR.jpg&h=26b2c1aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGod Save our Queen <br />\nGod Save Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQktVbj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQktVbj.png&h=b6f963c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uspeQKJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuspeQKJ.png&h=f65464a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MzVtVby.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMzVtVby.png&h=b6f62ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFIVE Demands, NOT ONE LESS!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMay she defend our laws,<br />\nAnd ever give us cause,<br />\nTo sing with heart and voice.<br />\nGod save the Queen."},{"pid":"f6c93e2c0003becf1ef1aa51ccba2e2c8a800394","tid":1566844,"uid":254330,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d145cf0c9d7517b28201e7a6164f1944651a6f","tid":1566844,"uid":283587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:51:40.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"c24d7a59aef3469e963ae1465b1ef68fb0742fa5","tid":1566844,"uid":135293,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e335cfde349fdd4a9a174557d27d3545d8e723","tid":1566844,"uid":135293,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c24d7a59aef3469e963ae1465b1ef68fb0742fa5","tid":1566844,"uid":135293,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282034f1591fb1684572ba6b84c3bde0f3cdbddd","tid":1566844,"uid":38904,"like":1